<section id="features" class="home-process-section">
  <div class="home-container">
    <h2 class="home-title">Do seu banco direto para a Blockchain.<br/><span class="gradient-text">Sem escalas.</span></h2>
    <p class="home-subtitle">
      Eliminamos os intermediários. O FlowPay conecta seu PIX diretamente à <strong>NEØ Smart Factory™</strong>.
      A fábrica opera 24/7 para converter seu valor em ativos digitais instantaneamente.
    </p>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3>Faça o PIX</h3>
        <p>Escolha o valor e pague com seu banco preferido. Simples como comprar café.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="step-connector">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="pulse-anim">
          <polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="step-card highlight">
        <div class="step-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
             <!-- Smart Factory / Chip Icon -->
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"></rect>
              <line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"></line><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"></line>
              <line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"></line><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"></line>
              <line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"></line><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"></line>
              <line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"></line><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gradient-text">A Smart Factory Processa</h3>
        <p>O motor industrial entra em ação. Validação, mintagem e alocação em milissegundos.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="step-connector">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="pulse-anim">
          <polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3>O Ativo é Seu</h3>
        <p>Recebido direto na sua carteira. Sem dias úteis, sem espera. Liquidez instantânea.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .home-process-section {
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .home-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .home-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .home-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-card {
    flex: 1;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  /* Highlight center card (Factory) */
  .step-card.highlight {
    background: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.05);
  }

  .step-icon-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: -10px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: #ff007a;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.5);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .step-card.highlight .step-icon {
    color: #ff007a;
    background: rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 122, 0.2);
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .step-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .step-connector {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 3.5rem; /* Align with icons */
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .pulse-anim {
    animation: pulse-right 1.5s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-right {
    0% { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 0.3; }
    50% { transform: translateX(5px); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .home-process-section {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .home-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .process-steps {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .step-connector {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      padding: 0;
      margin: -10px 0;
    }
    
    .step-card {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>

